They can also create products like live sessions (live courses, a bootcamp, a congress, a yoga class or even a concert) where they can spread their knowledge to a large group of people at the same time, and if they already have their course filmed, they can upload it as well as an online course that will sell on its own giving them time to create more content.  Also in Venn, they will have access to their DB at all time in just one click, (This is very important, because if they own their DB they own their teaching business) they can create landing pages for their products in just seconds without having to know coding, they can charge their student from all over the world, they don't need to remind their student of an upcoming class or sessions because the platform does it by itself automatically, they can teach their sessions inside our own video chat room for up to 300 students (No more sending zoom's links), they don't need to worry about time zones, since the platform does the scheduling automatically depending on the student's time zone, they can record their sessions to do with them later what they want, share it with their students, make pieces of content for social media to promote themselves or whatever they want, its their content anyway, so as you can see, according to testimonials of Venn users, before Venn they use to use 5 to 7 different platforms and a lot of time and attention just to make a one hour sessions, and now, they just use Venn and that's it.
